{
  "stem": "6110.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somehow, there was Jewish police at the entrance, you know, Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I always-- you know, I, I always knew how to talk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I always tell them, you know, I didn't sneak through a broken hole or through a basement.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was like-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the end of the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a section that was a Jewish neighborhood before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was all around, all around closed up, sure, sure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was closed up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the gate's wall, sometimes I was seeing two Germans, then the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the ghetto was in the hands of the Jewish police, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What can I tell you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't want to talk about my brothers and sisters not nice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes they were terrible, terrible, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but all right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could deal with them, no picnic, still deal with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't go too often, because wasn't so easy to go to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I didn't go too often.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, sure, he knew Mama, Mama.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then what I want say, then came a Judenrein.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know what's a Judenrein.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were throwing out the Jews from Skala.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was a horrible time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had to go and try to sneak in back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I should be with my family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went in, and I was staying with my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Meantime, they-- before that-- no, it was wrong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before I sneak in back to the ghetto, they kill my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took her out from the room and took her on the street, shot her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they killed her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How did I know?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
